# ROVEXO v1.0 — SPLASH SCREEN MASTER SPEC

**STATUS: CANONICAL | PRODUCTION READY | CERTIFIED**

**Exactly one Splash Screen.** Do not create duplicates.

Entry: `features/auth/components/SplashScreen.tsx` · `app/(auth)/splash/**` · `lib/auth/bootstrap.ts` · `AUTH_MASTER_SPEC.splash`

DOM: `data-auth-screen="splash"` · `data-auth-ui="v1.0-splash-ready"` · `data-splash-lock="CANONICAL"`

## Locked behaviour

- Show instantly (premium light background only — no dark mode)
- ROVEXO mark + wordmark + BUY. SELL. GROW. + fade-only load cue
- Timing: `minDisplayMs` 600 · `maxWaitMs` 1200 · soft exit fade 220ms
- Brand stage always opaque (SSR chrome + live overlay) — **never** opacity-0 blank paint
- Session: getSession → getUser (silent refresh/validate) → guest `/welcome` | verify-email | `/`
- Invalid/expired: local sign-out → guest (no token/error exposure)
- Motion: fade_only — **no** spinner string, scale, or bounce
- RX app icon mark allowed on Splash only
- PWA `start_url`: `/splash`

## Singularity

ONE splash · ONE session bootstrap (`resolveSplashDestination`) · ONE auth system.

## Do not touch

Login v1.0 and Register v1.0 remain FROZEN. Do not modify their UI or auth flows from Splash work.

## Allowed

Security · performance · a11y · responsive · bug · deployment fixes that preserve splash contract.

